Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try and gather\Nthe unrestrained winds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll run toward the horizon,\Nalongside the wave crests
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve made my decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if there’s a long way to go\Non that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll continue towards the future I’ve planned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time rushes us\NThe heartbeat speeds up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke in the middle of a dream\NI kept searching for that same light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:01:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the shining star-lit sky with\Ncountless constellations and shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something beyond that…\NWhat were you gazing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you gazing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encounter! The Boy With a Star's Name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizune!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a protection commission\Nfrom the Village Hidden in the Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some kind\Nof problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve never heard about it, Shizune?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Village Hidden in the Stars\Nis small in terms of scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are very proud and\Nhave often caused trouble…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will you accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t simply disregard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you-know-what\Nis in that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems they’ll form\Na three-man team
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Neji as the squad leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Village Hidden in the Stars\Nis a Shinobi village, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they should do\Ntheir own protecting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without asking others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are often instances\Nof a small village
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with friendly relations\Nseeking cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In particular, that village is small
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it seems there aren’t\Nthat many Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding. But why’s a place\Nlike that being targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all happened 200 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A star fell in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those stars like in the sky,\Nnot ninja stars or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! It seems\Nthere’s a mysterious power in the star
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that has an effect on Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a superstition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, no way has\Na star ever come falling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s actually been targeted\Nseveral times until now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by Shinobi of other lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Shinobi of other lands?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious power, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, it does seem that someone\Nlike Orochimaru would target it…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I guess I’ll be participating\Nin this one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But the three-man team’s\Nalready been determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got an ace up my sleeve…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amaguriama Sweet Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. I’ll take the lead from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s danger before\Nentering the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go on ahead and be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, what’s Naruto doing\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tsunade, there was a report
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Naruto has joined up\Nwith Neji’s squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I added him to\Nthe Village Hidden in the Stars mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those four proved themselves\Nin the Katabami Gold Mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and things will quiet down\Nin the village here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’d change an already determined\Nthree-man squad just for that reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tsunade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare Roasted Chestnut Bean Jelly\Nwith gold leaf candy from Amaguriama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that was from Naruto…?\N70.01	01:06:50:29	01:06:52:26	Tea! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don’t want to fall behind\Neveryone’s training…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing\Nduring your training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizura suddenly keeled\Nover in pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him to the medical treatment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hokuto by herself is\Nenough for an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru, you have a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I’m here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I cross this valley,\NI’ll be in the Land of Bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Village Hidden in the Stars\Nis close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Kujaku…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy blocked Kunai knives\Nwith Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy’s an enemy…\NHe suddenly attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re Leaf Shinobi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from\Nthe Village Hidden in the Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Sumaru.\NI came to pick you guys up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you do such a thing…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The border of the Land of Bears\Nis constantly filled with poison gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s also serves as\Na natural fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against invasion from other lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the danger\Nyou were talking about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that great, Naruto?\NYou owe Sumaru your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the beginning of\Na beautiful friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between the Leaf\Nand the Hidden Star Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it none of my concern?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have just watched\Nand not done anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Akahoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I serve as the deputy Hoshikage\Nof the Village Hidden in the Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy…Hoshikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the sudden passing\Nof the Third Hoshikage one year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,presently there is\Nno Hoshikage in this village…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I heard the only ones who can\Nrefer to themselves as a Kage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the leaders of\Nthe Five Great Hidden Villages…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn’t make any difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not inferior to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we’re small now,\Nthis village will someday rival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Hidden Villages of\Nthe Five Great Nations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time,\NI’ll become the true Hoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the training ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now of all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry about him.\NPlease continue your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As  you say, the Shinobi in our village\Nare not qualified
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to refer to themselves as a Kage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in this village,\Nthere is the star
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that all the Kage in the Five\NGreat Hidden Villages also envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will use the power\Nof the star and someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this can become a village which can\Nclaim the Sixth Kage title.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that star is being targeted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Our search team\Nobtained some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’d that guy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally caught up.\NWas your name Omaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Omaru, Sumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sumaru’s sure\Nan interesting name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s another name for\Nthe star cluster Pleiades or Spring Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in this village has\Na name associated with stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is a village\Nwhere a star fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you trying to elicit from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn’t thanked you for earlier, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell even if you give me\Nthe runaround…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people from other lands\Nare all after the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have that power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can stand above all\Nof the Hidden Villages, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your awesome Chakra\Nalso the power of the star?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had that star,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would everyone have\Nthe same Chakra as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The more tremendous the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more hard work is required\Nto control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll work hard, work hard, work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll become the Hoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I look forward to working\Nwith you at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m also going to become\Nthe Hokage someday, believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a strange guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the star!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they really are collapsed entirely\Nfrom the center towards the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a star explodes in mid-air,\Nit seems they collapse like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the training area\Nwhere the star is enshrined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and show me the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. People from other lands\Naren't allowed beyond this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the star is over there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t protect it\Nif I can’t get close to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like we trust you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you’re such a suspicious guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can’t you trust us\Nwho came here on a mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my personality, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be?! No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll chase him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go to your friends\Nin the training area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hokuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru… I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn’t protect the star…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s ridiculous to do something\Nlike steal in someone else’s village
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in broad daylight, you little thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I won’t let you getaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Kujaku…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Chakra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, oh! Move away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the Everywhere Shuriken Jutsu\Ntowards that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my real target!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found your weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main body doesn’t move\Nwhile controlling the Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go! Clone Body Slam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more ways to\Nuse my Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one hit hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Synthesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry. But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my mistake for\Nleaving it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for him,\Nhe used the same Ninja Art as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who perform\Nthe star training
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can use that Ninja Art…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you’re saying\Nhe’s someone from this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the one who let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll get the star back, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind blows, Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain,\NThe memories won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should be brought along?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble them into a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no second chance, never
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish it is to throw away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting so innocently, Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The images.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably will not end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably will not end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn that love-filled heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sail across a thousand dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running freely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To take hold of the world in hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clouds scatter
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun sets yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The solo parade begins to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adventure, Lucky Day, Heart Beat, Rising,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decisive, Encounter, Life, Mutual Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m kind of bothered by\Nthe village leader’s attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the opponent used\Nthe Ninja Art: Kujaku means…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the attacker is definitely\Na Shinobi from this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that old man didn’t say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there’s some kind\Nof secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to investigate him.\NLet’s all split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll get that star back,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next: “The Remembered Lullaby”
